14
00:02:26,553 --> 00:02:28,803
I didn't write any anonymous letter.

15
00:02:28,912 --> 00:02:29,552
I didn't do it,

16
00:02:29,553 --> 00:02:30,952
so I have to get to the bottom of this.

17
00:02:30,953 --> 00:02:31,952
Is this your attitude

18
