23
00:02:43,032 --> 00:02:44,803
I'll take full responsibility.

24
00:02:44,912 --> 00:02:46,203
But, what if it was not me?

25
00:02:46,833 --> 00:02:47,471
Under the condition

26
00:02:47,472 --> 00:02:48,352
of you not having any proof,

27
00:02:48,353 --> 00:02:49,803
you randomly

28
