00:38:17,232 --> 00:38:19,111
What makes you think I'll hurt her?

865
00:38:19,112 --> 00:38:21,071
Do I need to remind you who you are?

866
00:38:21,072 --> 00:38:21,711
Back at that time,

867
00:38:21,712 --> 00:38:23,432
I just borrowed ideas from Xu Miao

868
00:38:23,433 --> 00:38:24,631
for my own graduation project.

869
00:38:24,632 --> 00:38:26,243
How can you make it sound so pleasant?

870
00:38:26,353 --> 00:38:27,671
That's plagiarism.

871
00:38:27,672 --> 00:38:28,151
Fine.

872
00:38:28,152 --> 00:38:29,312
Even if it's plagiarism,

873
00:38:29,313 --> 00:38:32,442
there's no need
to judge me forever over it.

874
00:38:55,873 --> 00:38:57,402
Drinking so much coffee.

875
00:38:57,953 --> 00:38:59,402
Can your heart take it?

876
00:39:00,112 --> 00:39:00,912
Have some of this instead,

877
00:39:00,913 --> 00:39:02,123
for the vitamin C.

878
00:39:03,072 --> 00:39:03,922
I'm tired.

879
00:39:06,192 --> 00:39:07,922
Didn't sleep well again last night?

880
00:39:09,152 --> 00:39:11,402
It seems that I have reached the age

881
00:39:11,913 --> 00:39:14,603
that the sleep quality becomes terrible.

882
00:39:18,072 --> 00:39:20,362
I remember you saying

883
00:39:20,393 --> 00:39:22,282
you'd take time off

884
00:39:22,672 --> 00:39:24,203
after Dr. Gao graduates.

885
00:39:25,112 --> 00:39:26,043
Will you still take it?

886
00:39:27,393 --> 00:39:28,282
Yeah, I am.

887
00:39:30,152 --> 00:39:32,723
Then, submit your leave request
to me today.

888
00:39:34,232 --> 00:39:35,003
Alright.

889
00:40:47,820 --> 00:40:51,390
(Leave Application)

890
00:40:56,552 --> 00:40:57,442
Xiang Nan,

891
00:40:59,152 --> 00:41:02,083
no matter what you thought of me before,

892
00:41:02,552 --> 00:41:05,442
I would never use love as a transaction.

893
00:41:06,953 --> 00:41:08,243
Maybe you don't know,

894
00:41:09,032 --> 00:41:11,282
but my career in Japan wasn't smooth.

895
00:41:11,873 --> 00:41:12,832
Returning here, things weren't

896
00:41:12,833 --> 00:41:14,563
going well either.

897
00:41:15,993 --> 00:41:18,003
I was extremely depressed.

898
00:41:19,032 --> 00:41:20,591
When I was at a gathering,

899
00:41:20,592 --> 00:41:21,962
I met Jiaqiao.

900
00:41:23,112 --> 00:41:25,312
She's someone full of enthusiasm.

901
00:41:25,313 --> 00:41:26,563
She is just so contagious,

902
00:41:27,433 --> 00:41:29,882
and also very proactive,

903
00:41:30,353 --> 00:41:32,123
always pushing people forward.

904
00:41:34,433 --> 00:41:36,442
She motivated me a lot.

905
00:41:39,433 --> 00:41:40,312
Being able to have

906
00:41:40,313 --> 00:41:41,191
someone who's incredibly selfless

907
00:41:41,192 --> 00:41:44,442
like her is indeed difficult.

908
00:41:45,913 --> 00:41:47,243
I really cherish her.

909
00:41:51,192 --> 00:41:52,191
But, Jiang Hongbin

910
00:41:52,192 --> 00:41:53,882
will never approve.

911
00:41:54,672 --> 00:41:55,723
If I never try,

912
00:41:56,152 --> 00:41:57,882
how do I know the outcome?

913
00:42:00,473 --> 00:42:02,442
I can only say that you don't know him.

914
00:42:03,833 --> 00:42:04,842
Lv Liang!

915
00:42:05,232 --> 00:42:06,922
Lv Liang, lend me a hand.

916
00:42:09,712 --> 00:42:11,282
Xiang Nan, why are you here?

917
00:42:11,393 --> 00:42:12,243
Jiaqiao.

918
00:42:12,512 --> 00:42:14,243
What did you buy?

919
00:42:14,473 --> 00:42:15,992
Mops, dustpans,

920
00:42:15,993 --> 00:42:17,151
just all the necessary stuff.

921
00:42:17,152 --> 00:42:18,962
I bought all the necessary items.

922
00:42:19,152 --> 00:42:21,472
Didn't I tell you I'd order these online?

923
00:42:21,473 --> 00:42:22,591
You order it?

924
00:42:22,592 --> 00:42:23,551
You've been saying that
for a very long time.

925
00:42:23,552 --> 00:42:24,952
You always procrastinate.

926
00:42:24,953 --> 00:42:25,752
Anyway, it's no trouble.

927
00:42:25,753 --> 00:42:27,643
I bought them all on the way here.

928
00:42:27,953 --> 00:42:29,482
Let me check it.

929
00:42:30,473 --> 00:42:31,442
Let me see.

930
00:42:31,592 --> 00:42:32,523
Are you okay?

931
00:42:33,993 --> 00:42:35,523
I'm just kidding. Don't worry.

932
00:42:35,913 --> 00:42:36,643
Oh yeah!

933
00:42:36,672 --> 00:42:38,123
You can just put this over there.

934
00:42:38,192 --> 00:42:39,442
I'll tidy them up later.

935
00:42:41,552 --> 00:42:43,111
How strong you are!

936
00:42:43,112 --> 00:42:43,792
Be careful.

937
00:42:43,793 --> 00:42:44,523
Alright.

938
00:42:49,592 --> 00:42:51,523
Ms. Xiang.

939
00:42:51,632 --> 00:42:53,191
Did you come here
to assess him secretly?

940
00:42:53,192 --> 00:42:53,992
What do you think?

941
00:42:53,993 --> 00:42:55,322
Has he passed?

942
00:42:57,512 --> 00:42:59,683
Jiaqiao, tell me the truth.

943
00:43:00,313 --> 00:43:01,832
Did he tell you

944
00:43:01,833 --> 00:43:03,282
